RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select rate_code,rate_code_desc from lftms_standard_rate_code where rate_type='S'and record_stat='O'and auth_stat='A'

SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE, A.RATE_DESCR FROM LFTMS_RATE_CODE A, LFTMS_FLOAT_RATE_MASTER B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND B.CCY_CODE = ? AND A.BRANCH_CODE = sypks_utils.get_branch(?) AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE

select a.product_code, A.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION from oltms_product a, olvw_avl_prod_br_usr b where a.module = 'LB' and a.product_code = b.product_code and a.once_auth = 'Y'and b.branch_code = sypks_utils.get_branch(?) and b.user_id = GLOBAL.USER_ID and a.product_code in (select a.PRODUCT_CODE from LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD a,oltms_product b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c where a.PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code and a.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? and b.product_code = c.product and c.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT is not NULL and a.version_no = (SELECT max(version_no) from LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD where contract_Ref_no = ?)and c.product_type = 'L' AND NVL(C.LC_DRAWDOWN, 'N') = 'N' UNION select a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE from LBTBS_CONTRACT_BORR_DDPROD a,oltms_product b,OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c where a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code and a.contract_ref_no = ? and nvl(c.LC_DRAWDOWN, 'N') = 'N' and a.version_no = (select latest_version_no from OLTBS_CONTRACT where contract_ref_no = ?)and a.customer_no = ? and b.product_code = c.product and c.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT is not NULL)and a.product_code not in (select p.product from LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF p where p.product = a.product_code and NVL(p.SHOWN_IN_CONTRACT_MAIN_SCREEN, 'N') <> 'Y'and NVL(p.AMORTIZATION_CONST_COMPONENT, 'N') = 'Y' and NVL(p.STOP_APPLICATION, 'N') <> 'Y') order by a.product_code

SELECT a.contract_ref_no , a.user_ref_no, a.product_code, a.counterparty, a.contract_ccy, a.latest_event_seq_no, a.product_type, b.principal_outstanding_bal , g.facility_name, g.TRANCHE_REF_NO , d.product_description, f.short_name FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT a,OLTBS_CONTRACT_BALANCE b, OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER g , oltms_product d, oltms_customer f WHERE a.contract_ref_no = g.contract_ref_no AND a.latest_version_no = g.version_no AND a.contract_status = 'A' AND a.product_type = 'L'AND a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no AND a.module_code = 'LB' AND A.BRANCH=GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND g.LC_DRAWDOWN = 'N' AND NVL(g.swing_line,'N')='N' AND nvl(g.Ancillary, 'N') = 'N' AND a.product_code = d.product_code AND a.counterparty = f.customer_no AND f.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 from OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLLOVER e where e.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no AND e.version_no = a.latest_version_no AND e.roll_inst_status IN ('I','P')) AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM lbtbs_contract_merge_master m, lbtbs_contract_merge_detail n WHERE a.contract_ref_no = n.child_ref_no AND m.contract_ref_no = n.contract_ref_no AND m.merge_serial_no = n.merge_serial_no AND m.auth_stat = 'U') AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM lbtbs_contract_merge_master m WHERE a.contract_ref_no = m.contract_ref_no AND m.auth_stat = 'U') AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR WHERE product_code = a.product_code AND user_id = global.user_id) AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT k, OLVW_USER_PRODUCTS S WHERE S.USER_ID = global.user_id AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = k.PRODUCT_CODE AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = a.product_code) AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM smvws_user_branches b WHERE b.User_id = global.user_id AND b.Branch_code = a.branch) AND NOT EXISTS ( Select 1 from LFTB_MARGIN_REVN_ACTIVATED_CONT mrg where mrg.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no )

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LBTB_SPLIT_PRODUCT_INTCOMPS.COMPONENT = LBTBS_PARTIAL_ROLL_INTRATE_FIX.COMPONENT AND LBTB_SPLIT_PRODUCT_INTCOMPS.SERIAL_NO = LBTBS_PARTIAL_ROLL_INTRATE_FIX.SPLIT_NO AND LBTB_SPLIT_PRODUCT_INTCOMPS.SPLIT_SERIAL_NO = LBTBS_PARTIAL_ROLL_INTRATE_FIX.SPLIT_SERIAL_NO AND LBTB_SPLIT_PRODUCT_INTCOMPS.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_PARTIAL_ROLL_INTRATE_FIX.CONTRACT_REF_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC FROM (SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, B.FIELD_DESC AS RATE_CODE_DESC, A.AUTH_STAT AS AUTH_STAT, A.RECORD_STAT AS RECORD_STAT FROM LFTMS_TREASURY_RATE_CODE A, OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.FIELD_NAME AND B.MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'RTCD' AND A.RATE_CODE_USAGE = B.FIELD_TYPE UNION SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, A.RATE_DESCR AS RATE_CODE_DESC, A.AUTH_STAT AS AUTH_STAT, A.RECORD_STAT AS RECORD_STAT FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE A, CFTMS_FLOAT_RATE_MASTER B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND B.CCY_CODE = ? AND A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE UNION SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC, AUTH_STAT, RECORD_STAT FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE = 'S') WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY RATE_CODE

SELECT a.FREQUENCY,a.RATE_CODE,a.units,a.CCY_CODE FROM lFTM_TENOR_CODE_MAINT a,lftm_rate_code_maint b WHERE a.RATE_CODE=? AND a.CCY_CODE=? and a.rate_code = b.rate_code and a.ccy_code = b.ccy_code and b.auth_stat='A'

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LBTB_SPLIT_PRODUCT_INTCOMPS.COMPONENT = LBTBS_RATE_SETTING_RULES.COMPONENT AND LBTB_SPLIT_PRODUCT_INTCOMPS.SERIAL_NO = LBTBS_RATE_SETTING_RULES.SPLIT_NUMBER AND LBTB_SPLIT_PRODUCT_INTCOMPS.SPLIT_SERIAL_NO = LBTBS_RATE_SETTING_RULES.SPLIT_SERIAL_NO AND LBTB_SPLIT_PRODUCT_INTCOMPS.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_RATE_SETTING_RULES.CONTRACT_REF_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select distinct a.rate_code, a.rate_descr from cftms_rate_code a, cftms_float_rate_master b where a.rate_code = b.rate_code and a.record_stat = 'O' and a.auth_stat = 'A' and b.ccy_code = ? and a.branch_code = sypks_utils.get_branch(?) and a.branch_code = b.branch_code and ? = 'F' union select rate_code,rate_code_desc from lftms_standard_rate_code where rate_type='S' and record_stat='O' and auth_stat='A' and ? = 'X' UNION SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND TYPE = NVL(?,TYPE) ORDER BY RATE_CODE
SELECT FIELD_NAME, FIELD_DESC FROM OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS WHERE FIELD_TYPE = 'BA' and field_name ='BAPRODUCT' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O'AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
